divs: Sighting DetailsIn the summer of 97 I went to pick my car up with my parents at a shade tree type mechanich shop on north kern street. We seen a row of 6 to 8 lights in the sky for about 8 minutes. Then helicopters approached both sides of the lights and a couple minutes later it disapered and the helicopters left.
Summary: just a single row of lights
